mlops:MLOps rdfs:comment "A paradigm that extends DevOps practices to machine learning systems, focusing on the deployment, monitoring, and continuous improvement of ML models in production through techniques such as continuous integration, continuous deployment, continuous monitoring, and continuous training."@en .
mlops:ContinuousDeployment rdfs:comment "A practice within MLOps that automates the deployment of validated models to production environments."@en .
